 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to France Bleu, a network of local and regional radio stations in France, services on the Paris 13th metro line, which connects Paris to the suburb of Saint-Denis, were suspended between 12.52 p.m. and 2.30 p.m. local time (1052-1230GMT) due to a serious passenger accident.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France Bleu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\"}, {\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France Bleu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Bleu\"}, {\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9972717928795787, \"rank\": 0.0015611061665479755, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999086328486, \"rank\": 9.136724755954422e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999086328486, \"rank\": 9.136724755954422e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Denis_station\", \"score\": 0.9999341933535835, \"rank\": 3.1656595864404574e-05, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"ty